description: 0xTama is a pixelated pass NFT series under Janshi Club Collections of Mahjong Meta. In Mahjong Meta game, Tama acts as a loyal pet NFT for Mahjong Meta players to participate in automated strategic mahjong battles, while 0xTama functions as a pfp collection of Tama and also an on-chain certificate for players to activate their in-game special benefits. Each season, various perks, additional rewards, and future exclusive privileges will be provided to players who bind this NFT and actively participate in Mahjong Meta competitions.
